edu.cmu.cs.lane.datatypes

Class SampleLabelBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.cs.lane.datatypes.SampleLabelBean

  • public class SampleLabelBean
extends java.lang.Object
    The class SampleLabelBean represents for each sample a hash of clinical variables or sample labels (.e.g., disease state). Each label is represented as a String-pair containing variable id and information related to the variable (possibly as a JSON object if needed)
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
